`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- `@react-three/rapier`'s `CapsuleCollider` takes `args={[halfHeight, radius]}` where `halfHeight` is the cylindrical section half-height (excluding caps). For total height 1.8, radius 0.3: `halfHeight = (1.8 - 2*0.3) / 2 = 0.6`.
- The jest config's `transformIgnorePatterns` doesn't include `@react-three/rapier`, so tests must mock it — otherwise Jest will fail to parse ESM from the package.
